code: /**  * Get standard Kinesis-related config properties.  */ public static Properties getStandardProperties() {     Properties config = new Properties().     config.setProperty(AWSConfigConstants.AWS_REGION, "us-east-1").     config.setProperty(AWSConfigConstants.AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID, "accessKeyId").     config.setProperty(AWSConfigConstants.AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY, "secretKey").     return config. }
